name: Verify that user is able to navigate to try Editor page under Arrays in Python page
fullName: Arrays: Verify that user is able to navigate to try Editor page under Arrays in Python page

steps.name: Given  The user is logged with valid credential and the user is on the Home page
When  The user clicks the Get Started button in Array Panel
Then  The user should be navigated to the Array page
Given  The user is on the Arrays in Python page
When  The user clicks Try Here button in Arrays in Python page
Then  The user should be redirected to a page having a tryEditor with a Run button
